topologyContent.description:
Option 1: Direct Topology Content.
Provide the full containerlab topology YAML as a json string.
If this is provided, 'topologySourceUrl' MUST be empty.
{
	"topologyContent": {
	  "name": "your-lab-name",
	  "topology": {
		"kinds": {
		  "nokia_srlinux": {
			"type": "ixrd3",
			"image": "ghcr.io/nokia/srlinux"
		  }
		},
		"nodes": {
		  "srl1": {
			"kind": "nokia_srlinux"
		  },
		  "srl2": {
			"kind": "nokia_srlinux"
		  }
		},
		"links": [
		  {
			"endpoints": [
			  "srl1:e1-1",
			  "srl2:e1-1"
			]
		  }
		]
	  }
	}
  }
